title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast August 14: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks gained this week on muted mid-summer volumes. Consumer prices rose slightly less than expected and the market shrugged off a bigger-than-anticipated gain for the producer price index.
